name: KeyDownload
tag_list: monetization, optimization, free-software, social-apps, software-development, publishers, affiliates
overview:
KeyDownload is a high-tech company that develops, optimizes and distributes software, mobile applications and social apps, with an emphasis on social-sharing oriented products.

All of KeyDownload developments are based on a state-of-the-art installer designed by technology experts. KeyDownload’s sophisticated installer allows for a smoother installation process with more precise analytics data - providing both the user and software publisher with a better user experience.
